  <entry>
    <title>github博客(nexT主题)开启gitalk</title>
    <link href="http://blog.oiyou.net/2019/12/18/201912181600/"/>
    <id>http://blog.oiyou.net/2019/12/18/201912181600/</id>
    <published>2019-12-18T08:01:42.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-12-18T15:26:44.806Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="记录github博客开启gitalk"><a href="#记录github博客开启gitalk" class="headerlink" title="记录github博客开启gitalk"></a>记录github博客开启gitalk</h3><p>gitalk： 一个基于 Github Issue 和 Preact 开发的评论插件,方便用户交流</p><a id="more"></a><h4 id="准备工作"><a href="#准备工作" class="headerlink" title="准备工作"></a>准备工作</h4><p>注册github OAuth Apps <a href="https://github.com/settings/applications/new" target="_blank" rel="noopener">链接</a> </p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2019/12/18/g9uPEXhZvHa6DsG.png" alt="注册信息填写"></p><p>点击注册后跳转到成功页面</p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2019/12/18/niLWRtDcrmKuVae.png" alt="注册成功"></p><p>修改主题下配置文件(netx/_config.yml)</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">gitalk:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  github_id: github账号 # 如huangboo461</span><br><span class="line">  repo: 仓库名称 # 如huangboo461.github.io</span><br><span class="line">  client_id: Client ID # GitHub Application Client ID</span><br><span class="line">  client_secret: Client Secret # GitHub Application Client Secret</span><br><span class="line">  admin_user: github帐号 # 指定可初始化评论账户</span><br><span class="line">  distraction_free_mode: true</span><br><span class="line">  # 设置语言: en | es-ES | fr | ru | zh-CN | zh-TW</span><br><span class="line">  language: zh-CN</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>至此gitalk开启成功。</p><p>此时博客页面需要登录github初始化才行，并且每篇博客都要重新初始化，下篇介绍如何自动初始化。</p><p>参考地址 <a href="https://asdfv1929.github.io/2018/01/20/gitalk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> https://asdfv1929.github.io/2018/01/20/gitalk/ </a></p><p>注:参考以上地址开启gitalk时，发现使用最新next主题只需要配置即可。</p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;h3 id=&quot;记录github博客开启gitalk&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#记录github博客开启gitalk&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;记录github博客开启gitalk&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;记录github博客开启gitalk&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;gitalk： 一个基于 Github Issue 和 Preact 开发的评论插件,方便用户交流&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
